1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,840
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,840 --> 00:00:03,440
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,510 --> 00:00:05,280
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:05,780 --> 00:00:07,680
(BIT Logo Design Contest Voting:
Option A, Option B, Option C)

5
00:00:07,750 --> 00:00:09,380
(Jewelry Division,
Director Kim Myung Hui)

6
00:00:12,150 --> 00:00:13,150
What's the status?

7
00:00:13,420 --> 00:00:14,920
The voting is about to close.

8
00:00:16,090 --> 00:00:17,520
(Voting closed)

9
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:19,020
Voting is closed.

10
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,460
(Episode 19)

11
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:36,010
(Tallying results...)

12
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:37,940
(Winning Entry: Option C,
Congratulations!)

13
00:00:40,810 --> 00:00:42,780
Yes! You got first place!

14
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:54,530
No way.

15
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:07,940
The shareholders have voted,
and Chloe's symbol was selected.

16
00:01:08,010 --> 00:01:09,040
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

17
00:01:11,180 --> 00:01:13,210
You must have been short on time.

18
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,210
Did you design this yourself?

19
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:19,680
You gave me this task as a test
right from the start,

20
00:01:20,050 --> 00:01:21,420
so I had to show you what I've got.

21
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:24,120
Are you satisfied now?

22
00:01:26,620 --> 00:01:28,860
Don't take it personally.

23
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,200
When you're in my position,

24
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:33,630
you learn to be careful...

25
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:36,670
about who you bring on board.

26
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,070
The bio division,
with its new symbol,

27
00:01:40,770 --> 00:01:42,840
will now be restructured
as BIT Life.

28
00:01:44,510 --> 00:01:46,310
To move forward with the rebranding,

29
00:01:46,850 --> 00:01:48,780
I need you to resolve
my situation as well.

30
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:55,090
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

31
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,460
Manager Kang.

32
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:02,330
Appoint Director Kim Myung Hui...

33
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:05,900
as the president
of the bio division.

34
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:25,980
Chloe.

35
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:32,360
Don't read too much into it.

36
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:36,130
Our interests just aligned,
that's all.

37
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:40,730
If the situation changes,
we could end up on opposite sides.

38
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:44,400
Even so, I wanted to thank you.

39
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:47,640
Because for today, at least,
we're on the same side.

40
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:53,080
And even if things change,

41
00:02:53,410 --> 00:02:55,780
I hope we don't end up fighting.

42
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:05,520
A fight will be inevitable.

43
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:09,490
You have to protect the Adele Group
and Park Min Jun,

44
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,230
and I...

45
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:15,370
have to move on to my next plan.

46
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,740
- No way.
- The results are out.

47
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,770
What a bummer. I entered this too.

48
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,840
Wait, didn't they say
there were runner-up prizes?

49
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,910
(Kim Myung Hui,
Previous: Director of Adele Jewelry)

50
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:26,980
(Kim Myung Hui,
Now: President of BIT Life)

51
00:03:28,350 --> 00:03:29,350
You entered too, didn't you?

52
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,050
Excuse me. Just a moment.

53
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,050
Guess I didn't even make
the first cut.

54
00:03:36,690 --> 00:03:39,160
My gosh. Hey, what gives?

55
00:03:40,930 --> 00:03:43,160
- What the...
- For crying out loud.

56
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:45,030
- Oh my.
- Sorry about that.

57
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,270
- Why did she get first place?
- I'd like to see her design.

58
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:49,700
Let me get a photo of this too.

59
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,000
I can't believe
she's the president now.

60
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:54,170
(Now: President of BIT Life)

61
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,970
Of course she'd win first place.

62
00:04:02,950 --> 00:04:04,180
Get out of the way.

63
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:09,690
What?
Chloe's design won first place?

64
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:12,020
(Kim Myung Hui,
Now: President of BIT Life)

65
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,230
And on top of that,

66
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:17,530
Director Kim is now the president?

67
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:21,000
Why? Do you have a problem
with Chloe's abilities?

68
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:23,470
Please show some respect
to our president.

69
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:29,040
If Director Kim becomes president,

70
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,940
she won't be so desperate
for my family's shares.

71
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:35,850
If Min Jun's side
keeps delaying the wedding...

72
00:04:37,850 --> 00:04:41,750
and he keeps showing interest
in Chloe...

73
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:46,920
Where's Director Kim right now?

74
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,760
That's President Kim to you now.

75
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,060
And she's in a meeting.

76
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:55,870
She's incredibly busy
now that she's president.

77
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:59,270
There is absolutely no way
you can see her today.

78
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:16,420
So, is President Kim
really that busy?

79
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:20,460
I don't normally
pack her schedule that full.

80
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,760
Then why...

81
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,060
She's obviously...

82
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:26,160
going to make a scene
about rushing the wedding,

83
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,270
so I need to shut it down
while I have a good excuse.

84
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,640
I just want...

85
00:05:32,470 --> 00:05:35,040
President Kim to be happy,
even if it's only for today.

86
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:37,810
Yes!

87
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,920
Yes.

88
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,320
Choi Yu Na seemed really desperate.

89
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:54,130
Now that Kim Myung Hui is president,

90
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:56,630
she fears the wedding
might be called off.

91
00:05:56,730 --> 00:05:58,100
She must be getting antsy.

92
00:05:58,700 --> 00:06:01,470
Of course. I just knew it.

93
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:05,640
Isn't it the ideal time
to put our plan into motion?

94
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:09,840
This will be the first spark
we ignite between them.

95
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:14,110
We'll soon find out
whether Choi Yu Na...

96
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:16,050
can defy Park Tae Ho...

97
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,950
by ruining the wedding...

98
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:21,090
she's dreamed of.

99
00:06:58,220 --> 00:06:59,420
There you are.

100
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:02,060
Hey.

101
00:07:03,530 --> 00:07:05,230
I heard
about the symbol design contest.

102
00:07:06,030 --> 00:07:07,060
Congratulations.

103
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,400
I'll see you around.

104
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,540
Why are you avoiding me?

105
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:21,050
Have you...

106
00:07:22,210 --> 00:07:25,650
lost interest because
I'm not who you were hoping for?

107
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,620
That's enough.

108
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:36,760
This conversation
is making me uncomfortable.

109
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:44,670
Then...

110
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,870
give me a straight answer today.

111
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:52,580
You really don't want
to give us a shot at all?

112
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:00,890
You're such a coward.

113
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:07,190
I pour my heart out,
but you keep avoiding me.

114
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:08,630
Is a simple yes or no...

115
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:10,190
too much to ask?

116
00:08:11,530 --> 00:08:13,900
Is that why
you're not even fighting...

117
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:15,630
this marriage you don't want?

118
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:23,710
Not everyone has it
as easy as you do.

119
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,510
Giving answers and making choices...

120
00:08:26,210 --> 00:08:27,910
is difficult for some of us.

121
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:30,750
Does that really justify
avoiding it?

122
00:08:32,450 --> 00:08:35,090
Are you avoiding fights
because you think there's no point...

123
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:36,890
in living without her?

124
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:40,060
Could you actually tell her that...

125
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:42,330
with a straight face?

126
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:48,930
It's your choice
whether you have the wedding or not,

127
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,570
but you should ask yourself
if it's a cowardly...

128
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,740
and shameful one.

129
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:10,450
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

130
00:09:16,130 --> 00:09:17,630
You've worked so hard for this.

131
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:23,270
This is just the first opportunity
I've managed to create.

132
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:27,100
I need to get results in this role
and earn recognition...

133
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:30,510
so that Min Jun can be seen
as the rightful heir.

134
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,880
Exactly.

135
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:35,010
I can already tell
being president...

136
00:09:35,010 --> 00:09:36,810
carries more weight
than being a director.

137
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,520
The other executives on the board
are already buzzing about it.

138
00:09:41,850 --> 00:09:44,220
And Ms. Choi is getting antsy
about the wedding.

139
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:46,620
You ran into Ms. Choi?

140
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:50,030
She freaked out
about your presidency announcement.

141
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:51,230
Now that you're president,

142
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:54,000
she seems worried
you might call off the marriage.

143
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:57,130
Speaking of which,

144
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,800
what will you do
about Min Jun's wedding?

145
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:01,440
You don't have any more excuses
to put it off.

146
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:05,340
Then I'll have to find a way
to buy more time...

147
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:09,710
until we rebrand the bio division
and gain some leverage.

148
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:12,850
Only then can I sway Chairman Park
to call off the engagement...

149
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:16,190
and find another way
to get Dr. Baek's shares back.

150
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:18,890
You think Ms. Choi will sit back
and let that happen?

151
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:45,680
Come on, what now?

152
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:49,320
I'm so furious, I could explode.

153
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:52,190
If I don't let it out,
this anger is going to kill me.

154
00:10:52,890 --> 00:10:55,190
How could that tramp
become president?

155
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:56,460
How?

156
00:10:56,530 --> 00:11:00,530
Jung Ran, please. That's enough.

157
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:09,040
A mistress as a group president?

158
00:11:09,570 --> 00:11:13,110
You dare try to take my son's place
and run the group?

159
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:16,910
If you're that bitter,
take it up with the chairman.

160
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:19,820
You shameless tramp.

161
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,820
Then again,

162
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:27,090
you even got the board involved
to stop me,

163
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,930
so you must be fuming.

164
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:30,530
But...

165
00:11:31,060 --> 00:11:34,470
I'll never lose to you,
no matter what you try to pull.

166
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:40,200
Watch me closely
and see how high I rise.

167
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:45,410
You...

168
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:50,250
Jung Ran, that's about enough.
You really let off some steam.

169
00:11:51,950 --> 00:11:53,320
Let's go.

170
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:56,290
If you break down over this,
it'll only hurt you in the end.

171
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,760
Come on.

172
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:24,950
My gosh.

173
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:29,290
That vicious tramp!

174
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,560
Fine.

175
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:33,890
You're not even hiding
your greed anymore.

176
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:35,530
Mark my words.

177
00:12:35,590 --> 00:12:38,460
Whatever you get,
I'll take it all from you.

178
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,530
Adele Group,

179
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:42,300
the presidency,

180
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,700
and even her in-laws' shares?

181
00:12:57,950 --> 00:12:59,250
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

182
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,750
All she did was design
one lousy symbol.

183
00:13:28,310 --> 00:13:29,480
Do you like them?

184
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:35,390
Even if you really like them,
please don't steal them.

185
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,190
Why would I steal junk like this?

186
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,930
That's what you say,
but your eyes and hands...

187
00:13:46,230 --> 00:13:48,030
tell a different story.

188
00:13:50,830 --> 00:13:54,040
Watch where you're looking,
and keep your hands to yourself.

189
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:57,710
Because when someone steals from me,

190
00:13:57,710 --> 00:13:59,340
I do the same thing right back.

191
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,550
The exact same thing?

192
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,610
Meaning...

193
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:07,750
I might just steal something
from you too.

194
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:10,190
For example,

195
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:12,760
Park Min Jun.

196
00:14:13,690 --> 00:14:15,530
Park Min Jun is my fiance.

197
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,100
It's not like you two are in love.

198
00:14:22,970 --> 00:14:25,740
If you mess with my wedding,

199
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:29,110
I'll make you pay.

200
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:32,380
Fine. Go ahead and marry him.

201
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:35,210
That won't stop me
from having fun with him.

202
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:19,890
I couldn't sleep a wink
after our call yesterday.

203
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:23,430
I stayed up all night
picking out your gift,

204
00:15:23,430 --> 00:15:24,430
and I chose this.

205
00:15:24,930 --> 00:15:27,560
A five-carat, pear-shaped diamond.

206
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:30,200
Why are you giving this to me?

207
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:33,500
Think of it as a proposal.

208
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:37,610
I'd love for you and my son
to be together.

209
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:44,980
Things got a little heated last time
with your parents,

210
00:15:45,050 --> 00:15:46,120
but you know how it is.

211
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:48,820
One minute we're pulling hair
and grabbing collars,

212
00:15:48,890 --> 00:15:49,890
and the next we're holding hands...

213
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:52,390
and setting a wedding date.

214
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:54,930
I'm not so sure.

215
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:58,660
I don't just go for anything
that comes my way.

216
00:15:59,330 --> 00:16:00,430
Anything?

217
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:05,500
Come on,
let's not embarrass each other.

218
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:08,610
Let's be honest.
What you really want...

219
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:11,210
isn't Park Min Jun but Adele.

220
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:13,240
You don't seem like the type
to believe...

221
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:14,880
in something as naive as love.

222
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:20,450
You think Park Min Jun has an edge
because he's the eldest son?

223
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,550
He's still just a mistress's son.

224
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:25,360
In the end, Hyun Jun is the one...

225
00:16:25,690 --> 00:16:27,490
who'll run the Adele Group.

226
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:28,690
We'll see about that.

227
00:16:28,990 --> 00:16:30,590
There's no way
to know that for sure.

228
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:34,430
You only reached out
because you're scared...

229
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:35,830
now that Director Kim is president.

230
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:40,300
With the presidency and my shares,
she'll be too powerful for you.

231
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:44,580
Doesn't that just prove
how tight the succession race is?

232
00:16:48,350 --> 00:16:50,710
And for the record,
I'm a very greedy person.

233
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:53,650
I plan to have it all.
Adele and that so-called...

234
00:16:53,650 --> 00:16:54,950
"naive love."

235
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:59,520
I've walked through hellfire
to get this far.

236
00:17:01,530 --> 00:17:06,100
I'm not about to get tangled up
with a punk like Park Hyun Jun.

237
00:17:07,770 --> 00:17:08,770
Hey!

238
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:12,940
Did you just call my son a punk?

239
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:17,340
You think owning a few shares
makes you somebody.

240
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,440
If they weren't fighting so hard
over the succession,

241
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:22,410
those shares would be worthless.

242
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:25,620
I wouldn't pay a dime for them.

243
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,720
As if you're worthy
of marrying into this family,

244
00:17:28,120 --> 00:17:30,190
let alone getting
a pear-shaped diamond.

245
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:31,860
Regardless, for now,

246
00:17:32,390 --> 00:17:34,690
you need my family's shares.

247
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:39,530
Not that a punk like Park Hyun Jun
will ever be the successor anyway.

248
00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:42,930
Who do you think
you're talking smack about?

249
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:44,800
Do I need to drag you by the hair
like I did your mother...

250
00:17:44,870 --> 00:17:46,100
and knock some sense into you?

251
00:17:46,470 --> 00:17:49,540
I'm not holding back today,
so brace yourself, you brat.

252
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:52,710
I never lose a hair-pulling fight.

253
00:17:52,710 --> 00:17:53,740
You tramp!

254
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:56,880
Are you kidding me? Bring it!

255
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:59,550
- Let go, darn it.
- Let go.

256
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:02,450
You barely have any hair as it is!

257
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:04,120
Jung Ran!

258
00:18:05,290 --> 00:18:06,290
Let her go.

259
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:09,660
- Honestly, this is...
- Let go of me!

260
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:13,760
Jung Ran! For crying out loud...

261
00:18:14,670 --> 00:18:17,200
- My hair... Come here!
- Enough!

262
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:29,310
Unbelievable.

263
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:33,520
Tell me.
Why do I have to put up with this?

264
00:18:36,290 --> 00:18:39,320
It looks to me like you gave
as good as you got.

265
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,130
Good grief.

266
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:45,330
Goodness.

267
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:52,570
I've seen you
in plenty of catfights,

268
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:56,470
but this is the first time
I've ever seen you with a bruise.

269
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:57,980
Ten years...

270
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:01,710
No, if I were five years younger,
I wouldn't have been so humiliated.

271
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:05,150
This is what you get for meddling
in other people's marriages.

272
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:08,320
Her family's not that great,
and she's no catch either.

273
00:19:09,050 --> 00:19:10,990
Her family has shares!

274
00:19:11,050 --> 00:19:14,690
Don't get so focused on the shares
that you get crushed.

275
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:18,730
Just let Hyun Jun marry
the girl he actually likes...

276
00:19:18,730 --> 00:19:22,270
and live happily ever after.

277
00:19:22,330 --> 00:19:24,400
There you go again
with your idealistic nonsense.

278
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:27,200
Even high and mighty
Kim Myung Hui...

279
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:29,410
is arranging a marriage
for her only son,

280
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:32,080
and you're going on...

281
00:19:32,210 --> 00:19:34,440
about "happily ever after?"

282
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,650
As if. Ouch, my back!

283
00:19:37,050 --> 00:19:39,180
My back's killing me.

284
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:40,520
I can't believe this.

285
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:50,690
This just caused
a lot of unnecessary trouble.

286
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:54,060
We need to deal
with this wedding issue quickly.

287
00:19:56,370 --> 00:19:58,500
You said we'd reschedule
the family gathering...

288
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,640
after it fell apart.

289
00:20:01,710 --> 00:20:03,770
Invite my family over tonight.

290
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:11,010
If you do nothing
after this humiliation,

291
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:13,880
I won't be responsible
for what I do next.

292
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:16,550
I understand,
but tonight is just impossible.

293
00:20:16,950 --> 00:20:18,960
Nothing's prepared.
How can we possibly...

294
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:21,120
We can keep it simple.

295
00:20:21,430 --> 00:20:22,760
We'll sit down for a meal...

296
00:20:23,530 --> 00:20:25,630
and set a wedding date.

297
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,700
And tell my wife
to make herself scarce.

298
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:44,150
Wait, so I'm supposed to leave?

299
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:47,080
Those are the chairman's orders.

300
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:48,750
Tell him to forget it!

301
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:51,560
I am the lady of this house.

302
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:55,060
Hey, why are you yelling at Mrs. Ok?

303
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,030
She's just following
Chairman Park's orders.

304
00:20:57,660 --> 00:21:00,400
You just attacked Ms. Choi
and her parents.

305
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:02,970
If you stay, you'll start a fight,
so please go.

306
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:07,640
Come on, let's go shopping.
You love it.

307
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:09,410
I don't want to. I'm not leaving.

308
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:12,310
Why should I leave? Darn it.

309
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:14,380
I'm the lady of this house!

310
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:23,390
Mom, stop pouting.

311
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:25,890
That's not the right attitude
for a family dinner.

312
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:28,990
Since when do you have eyes
in the back of your head?

313
00:21:29,590 --> 00:21:31,130
Come on, now.

314
00:21:31,230 --> 00:21:34,300
Since we're trying
the family dinner again,

315
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:36,000
let's go in with a good attitude.

316
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,840
Unbelievable. You're so spineless.

317
00:21:38,970 --> 00:21:41,410
You might as well
hand over your pride too.

318
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:43,810
And Yu Na,

319
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:45,940
you're sure about this, right?

320
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:47,810
If he fails to show up again...

321
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,650
Mom, I told you not to worry.

322
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:52,580
This time,

323
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:55,050
I'm definitely going to lock down
a wedding date.

324
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:57,950
So,

325
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,690
stop grumbling and get ready.

326
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:04,430
Yes, this is the one.

327
00:22:04,630 --> 00:22:06,600
I knew I was in good hands.

328
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:08,970
You think she has fashion sense?

329
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:11,770
Like this is any good.
Her taste is terrible.

330
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:14,100
Why else would she choose Min Jun?

331
00:22:14,100 --> 00:22:15,110
Mom!

332
00:22:15,170 --> 00:22:16,170
What?

333
00:22:18,580 --> 00:22:21,550
Unbelievable.
You never let me have the last word.

334
00:22:21,910 --> 00:22:24,080
Honestly.

335
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:27,220
Ms. Oh, why do you keep
dragging me into it?

336
00:22:27,650 --> 00:22:30,190
Look, your shopping has
nothing to do with my card,

337
00:22:30,190 --> 00:22:31,320
so don't threaten me.

338
00:22:31,690 --> 00:22:34,220
Just use this as an excuse and
go wild with Chairman Park's card.

339
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,960
Look, I'm hanging up.

340
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:44,170
You came all the way to my office?

341
00:22:44,570 --> 00:22:46,340
What a pleasant surprise.

342
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:48,740
Were you on the phone?

343
00:22:49,410 --> 00:22:50,910
Yes, with my mom.

344
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,510
You know my family situation
is complicated, right?

345
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:56,650
I'm aware of the situation
with the two wives.

346
00:22:57,910 --> 00:23:01,120
Then again, the story is too famous
not to know.

347
00:23:01,650 --> 00:23:03,150
That's why there's always drama.

348
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:06,360
Looks like everyone's...

349
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,860
getting together at the house today
to talk about Min Jun's wedding.

350
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:11,130
They're probably trying
to pick a date.

351
00:23:13,060 --> 00:23:14,060
Really?

352
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:38,090
If I'm seen walking in with a girl,
it'll be a headache for everyone.

353
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:40,260
Thanks for helping me.

354
00:23:44,530 --> 00:23:45,630
Just make sure we don't get caught.

355
00:23:52,970 --> 00:23:53,970
I'm sorry.

356
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:57,840
Just help me one more time,

357
00:23:58,610 --> 00:23:59,740
like you did before.

358
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:04,750
What's this?
Keep staring and I might get ideas.

359
00:24:05,420 --> 00:24:06,420
Don't tell me...

360
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:08,920
you came here
just to gaze at me like that.

361
00:24:10,450 --> 00:24:12,860
Come to think of it, I wanted...

362
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:15,860
to thank you for the shoes
and apologize.

363
00:24:17,990 --> 00:24:19,360
How does lunch sound?

364
00:24:30,710 --> 00:24:31,740
Here you go.

365
00:24:32,810 --> 00:24:36,250
Lunch seems a bit light
for how sorry and grateful you are.

366
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:39,380
How about a nice dinner
after work instead?

367
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,860
Is there something out there?

368
00:24:45,390 --> 00:24:46,460
This pathway.

369
00:24:46,890 --> 00:24:49,460
Don't you have to go through here
to get to and from the office?

370
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:52,830
Pretty much, given the location.

371
00:24:54,930 --> 00:24:55,930
Why do you ask?

372
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,600
Are you worried people will think...

373
00:24:57,970 --> 00:25:00,800
there's something going on
between us?

374
00:25:02,670 --> 00:25:04,270
I don't mind the rumors,

375
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:06,810
or the idea of us having a thing.

376
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,230
Out of all places,

377
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:00,130
and with me of all people,

378
00:26:02,130 --> 00:26:03,570
what were you planning to do?

379
00:26:06,670 --> 00:26:08,470
I really feel like I was just used.

380
00:26:09,470 --> 00:26:10,570
It's not like that.

381
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,780
You're even more interesting
when you're flustered.

382
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:45,980
Don't try so hard
to get Min Jun's attention.

383
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:49,110
He's already giving you plenty.

384
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,380
And of course,

385
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,320
so am I.

386
00:26:58,190 --> 00:26:59,420
That said,

387
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:02,690
maybe you should reconsider this
more objectively.

388
00:27:03,890 --> 00:27:07,160
Instead of the guy
who sees you as someone else,

389
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,630
there's someone
who's curious about you...

390
00:27:10,470 --> 00:27:11,500
and wants to get to know you.

391
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:14,600
Aren't I a better catch?

392
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:21,580
Try giving that some thought.

393
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:23,380
As for that apology,

394
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:27,720
I'll collect on it later
with a real date.

395
00:27:29,650 --> 00:27:30,750
You can give me your answer then.

396
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:05,160
So what is it that you want from me?

397
00:28:05,990 --> 00:28:08,320
Am I supposed to take her place,
letting you hold me,

398
00:28:09,290 --> 00:28:10,590
and holding you in return?

399
00:28:13,930 --> 00:28:16,100
Does that really justify
avoiding it?

400
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:19,870
Are you avoiding fights because
you think there's no point...

401
00:28:19,970 --> 00:28:21,500
in living without her?

402
00:28:21,910 --> 00:28:23,840
Could you actually tell her that...

403
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:26,280
with a straight face?

404
00:28:27,540 --> 00:28:30,450
It's your choice
whether you have the wedding or not,

405
00:28:30,780 --> 00:28:32,850
but you should ask yourself
if it's a cowardly...

406
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,250
and shameful one.

407
00:29:06,020 --> 00:29:07,420
Is he still not picking up?

408
00:29:09,490 --> 00:29:10,490
I'm afraid so.

409
00:29:11,390 --> 00:29:13,060
He really needs to be here on time.

410
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,660
You texted him.

411
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,390
He'll come as soon as he sees it.

412
00:29:24,300 --> 00:29:25,700
It looks like Min Jun
is running a little late.

413
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:27,300
Please have some tea while we wait.

414
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:33,410
We're setting a wedding date today,
no matter what.

415
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:36,510
I'll wait all night for him
if I have to.

416
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,180
Goodness!

417
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,750
Min Jun.

418
00:29:43,050 --> 00:29:44,750
Min Jun, you're here.

419
00:29:45,190 --> 00:29:48,090
Finally, we get to sit down
and chat today.

420
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,290
Come on now, plop yourself down.

421
00:29:51,390 --> 00:29:53,760
I mean, please take a seat.

422
00:29:55,530 --> 00:29:58,170
Let's set our wedding date
before we eat.

423
00:30:02,410 --> 00:30:04,440
Don't just stand there, sit down.

424
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:11,920
I'm sorry,

425
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:14,050
but I have to call off...

426
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:16,190
the wedding.

427
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:24,590
What?

428
00:31:02,770 --> 00:31:05,800
(Pearl in Red)

429
00:31:06,170 --> 00:31:07,640
I won't back down.

430
00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:10,170
Do you know what I had to do
to make this wedding happen?

431
00:31:10,170 --> 00:31:11,810
To have you, I...

432
00:31:11,910 --> 00:31:12,910
Ms. Choi!

433
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:15,110
That's it.
Ever since Chloe showed up,

434
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:17,010
Min Jun and his mom have changed.

435
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:19,080
I need to remove Chloe from Adele
for good.

436
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:21,120
The new BIT Life symbol.

437
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,720
They stole it from me,
just an unknown designer.

438
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:25,660
Those are false accusations
and slander.

439
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,120
Whether it's true or not,

440
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:29,330
if you don't handle this properly,

441
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:31,330
you'll be fired as president...

442
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:33,900
and completely cut off
from the company.

443
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,300
Mark my words.

444
00:31:36,330 --> 00:31:38,330
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
